PersonalTutor is an extension layer built on top of DeepTutor. The upstream
DeepTutor source tree is preserved in the `deeptutor/` and `deeptutor_cli/`
packages and is intentionally kept in sync with upstream via `git rebase`.
All modifications to the upstream tree are isolated in the `patches/`
directory; the bulk of PersonalTutor's own code lives under `personal_tutor/`.
